articles.title: A YEAR IN REVIEW
articles.content: As dawn broke on this year, I was excited for a fresh start. Last year, I dealt with panic attacks and anxiety from taking on too many projects, a breakup that left me heartbroken, and a mini-identity crisis from settling down.

articles.title: My trip in Thailand
articles.content: I went to Thailand with my friend this Summer. It is really a great trip and I would like to share my story to you.I spent one week travelling the country. Chingmai was my first stop.
